title: The.Amazing.Race.Aus.S03E04.Aus.vs.NZ.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description:
The remaining eight teams cross from Cambodia to Thailand on foot and face a long bus ride to get to their destination. Aston and Christie struggle with each other, as well as the Race tasks.

Folks, I regret to say, this will be the last Amazing Race AU episode I am able to cap and post :-(
I am too far behind on my other work and the circumstances have become to tough to continue.
I will be stopping indefinitely from Saturday 12am Sydney Australia time.
